00:23:10,290 --> 00:23:11,610
was being done by this team,

628
00:23:11,610 --> 00:23:14,100
and this is what the
code snippet was doing.

629
00:23:14,100 --> 00:23:16,800
This change is causing
this to happen, right?

630
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:18,630
So being able to fully embed the context

631
00:23:18,630 --> 00:23:20,160
of what we're describing here,

632
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:21,240
I think we'll do two things.

633
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:25,080
One, we'll get away
from this idea of wolf,

634
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:26,610
the boy who cried wolf all the time,

635
00:23:26,610 --> 00:23:28,710
of random anomaly alerts that you ignore,

