00:24:46,980 --> 00:24:49,080
and it was caused by a
code change in Terraform

674
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:50,850
or in application logic,

675
00:24:50,850 --> 00:24:53,010
why can't we just raise
the PR automatically?

676
00:24:53,010 --> 00:24:55,500
And we still rely on the engineer

