00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:59,100
to actually approve the PR,
test it, and then merge it in,

678
00:24:59,100 --> 00:25:00,660
but at least get them all the way there,

679
00:25:00,660 --> 00:25:02,700
or at least give them the logging

